# C S L THUYT

## 1\. Mc tiu

Mc tiu ca d n "clone Spotify" s dng React, Python v Django, c th tm gn li mt s mc tiu chnh sau:

- Hiu r trit l v li ch ca phn mm m ngun m (PMNM): Mn hc nhm gip bn nm bt c cc khi nim ct li ca PMNM, lch s pht trin, cc loi giy php ph bin (v d: MIT, Apache, GPL), v nhng li ch m PMNM mang li cho c ngi dng v nh pht trin (tnh minh bch, cng ng h tr ln, kh nng ty bin cao, chi ph tim nng thp hn).  

- Nm vng quy trnh pht trin phn mm m ngun m: Bn s c lm quen vi cch mt d n m ngun m c xy dng v duy tr, bao gm vic ng gp m ngun, bo co li, tham gia vo cng ng, v qun l d n.  

- p dng kin thc v cc cng ngh c th trong bi cnh m ngun m: Vic la chn React (mt th vin JavaScript m ngun m), Python (mt ngn ng lp trnh m ngun m), v Django (mt framework web Python m ngun m) cho d n "clone Spotify" s gip bn hiu cch cc cng ngh m ngun m ny c s dng trong thc t  xy dng mt ng dng hon chnh.  

- Pht trin k nng thc hnh xy dng ng dng web full-stack: D n "clone Spotify" i hi bn phi lm vic c  frontend (React) v backend (Django/Python), cng nh tng tc vi c s d liu. iu ny gip bn rn luyn k nng pht trin ng dng web ton din.  

- Lm quen vi quy trnh lm vic nhm v qun l d n (nu lm vic nhm): Nu bn thc hin d n ny theo nhm, mn hc cng c th hng n vic pht trin k nng lm vic nhm, phn chia cng vic, qun l tin , v s dng cc cng c h tr cng tc (v d: Git, GitHub/GitLab).  

- Hiu v cc kha cnh php l v cng ng ca PMNM: Mn hc c th  cp n tm quan trng ca vic tun th giy php m ngun m v cch tng tc hiu qu vi cng ng m ngun m.  

- Khuyn khch t duy sng to v kh nng gii quyt vn : D n "clone Spotify" l mt bi ton thc t, i hi bn phi a ra cc quyt nh thit k, gii quyt cc vn  k thut pht sinh, v tm kim cc gii php hiu qu.  

Tm li, mc tiu ca mn hc ny khng ch l gip bn xy dng mt ng dng "clone Spotify" m cn trang b cho bn nhng kin thc v k nng cn thit  lm vic hiu qu vi cc d n phn mm m ngun m trong tng lai. Chc bn c mt tri nghim hc tp th v v thnh cng vi d n ca mnh!

## 2\. M t tng qut v h thng xy dng

H thng clone Spotify ny tp trung vo vic qun l v cung cp tri nghim nghe nhc, bao gm:

- Qun l th vin nhc: T chc mt kho tng m nhc khng l vi cc bi ht, album, ngh s, th loi khc nhau. D liu ny c sp xp mt cch khoa hc, cho php ngi dng d dng tm kim v khm ph.
- Qun l ngi dng: H tr ngi dng ng k ti khon, ng nhp v qun l thng tin c nhn. C th bao gm cc tnh nng nh to playlist c nhn, theo di ngh s yu thch, v xem lch s nghe nhc.
- Chc nng pht nhc: Cung cp kh nng pht trc tuyn cc bi ht vi cht lng m thanh tt. Cc tnh nng iu khin c bn nh pht/tm dng, chuyn bi, tua nhanh/tua li, iu chnh m lng l khng th thiu.
- Tm kim v khm ph: Cho php ngi dng d dng tm kim cc bi ht, ngh s hoc album theo t kha. ng thi, h thng c th gi  nhc da trn s thch, lch s nghe hoc cc playlist c to sn.
- Qun l playlist: Ngi dng c kh nng to, chnh sa v chia s cc playlist nhc c nhn.

Vi giao din ngi dng trc quan v d s dng (c xy dng bng React), h thng clone Spotify mang n s thun tin trong thao tc, gip ngi dng d dng tip cn v tn hng m nhc. Phn backend mnh m (xy dng bng Python v framework Django) m bo vic qun l d liu hiu qu, x l cc yu cu t ngi dng mt cch nhanh chng v n nh, ng thi c kh nng m rng  p ng lng ngi dng ngy cng tng.

H thng c xy dng vi tiu ch linh hot, d dng b sung cc tnh nng mi v iu chnh  ph hp vi nhu cu v mong mun ca ngi dng yu m nhc.

Kin trc h thng:

- Nghin cu v kin trc client-server: Hiu r cch frontend React gi yu cu n backend Django API v nhn d liu.
- Phn tch cch cc thnh phn tng tc: M t lung d liu gia frontend, backend v c s d liu cho cc tnh nng chnh (v d: pht mt bi ht, tm kim).
- Cn nhc v kin trc microservices (nu c  nh m rng trong tng lai): Mc d c th khng nm trong phm vi trin khai hin ti, nhng vic nghin cu s b v kin trc ny c th hu ch cho phn tho lun v kh nng m rng.

## Hng gii quyt d kin

Tip cn theo tng giai on:

- Giai on 1: Nghin cu v Lp k hoch chi tit:
  - Nghin cu su hn v cc tnh nng ct li ca Spotify: Phn tch lung ngi dng, cc API (nu c thng tin cng khai), v cch d liu c hin th.
  - Thit k kin trc h thng  mc  tng quan: V s  cc thnh phn chnh (React frontend, Django REST API backend, Database) v cch chng tng tc.
  - Lp k hoch pht trin chi tit: Chia nh d n thnh cc task nh hn, xc nh cng ngh c th cho tng phn (v d: th vin UI cho React, ORM cho Django), v c tnh thi gian thc hin.
  - Xy dng wireframe/mockup giao din ngi dng (UI/UX) c bn: Hnh dung giao din chnh ca ng dng.
- Giai on 2: Pht trin Backend (Django REST API):
  - Thit k schema c s d liu: Xc nh cc bng cn thit (Bi ht, Ngh s, Album, Ngi dng, Playlist) v mi quan h gia chng.
  - Xy dng Models trong Django: nh ngha cc model tng ng vi schema c s d liu.
  - Pht trin API Endpoints bng Django REST Framework: Xy dng cc API cho cc chc nng chnh nh ly danh sch bi ht, tm kim, to/xem playlist, qun l ngi dng (ng k, ng nhp c bn).
  - Trin khai cc logic nghip v c bn  backend: V d: x l tm kim, thm bi ht vo playlist.
- Giai on 3: Pht trin Frontend (React):
  - Thit lp mi trng pht trin React.
  - Xy dng cc components giao din ngi dng: To cc component hin th danh sch bi ht, thng tin bi ht ang pht, thanh iu khin nhc, v.v.
  - Kt ni vi Backend API: S dng fetch hoc cc th vin HTTP client khc (v d: Axios)  gi cc API  xy dng  backend.
  - Qun l state  frontend: S dng useState, useContext hoc cc th vin qun l state phc tp hn nu cn.
  - X l tng tc ngi dng: X l cc s kin nh click nt pht, tm dng, tm kim, thm vo playlist.
- Giai on 4: Kim th v Hon thin:
  - Vit unit tests cho backend (Django) v component tests cho frontend (React).
  - Kim th tch hp gia frontend v backend.
  - Sa li v ti u ha hiu sut.
  - Hon thin giao din ngi dng v tri nghim ngi dng.
- Giai on 5: Vit Bo co:
  - H thng ha cc kin thc  nghin cu v qu trnh pht trin.
  - Trnh by cc quyt nh thit k, cc vn   gp phi v cch gii quyt.
  - nh gi kt qu t c so vi mc tiu ban u.
  -  xut cc hng pht trin tip theo.

Cc cng c v th vin h tr:

- Frontend (React): S dng cc th vin UI component c sn  tit kim thi gian pht trin giao din.
- Backend (Django): Tn dng cc tnh nng mnh m ca Django nh ORM, qun l ngi dng (nu cn), v Django REST Framework  xy dng API nhanh chng.
- Qun l d n: S dng cc cng c qun l d n (v d: Trello, Asana)  theo di tin  v qun l cng vic.
- Kim sot phin bn: S dng Git v cc nn tng nh GitHub hoc GitLab  qun l m ngun.

## Cng c v mi trng pht trin

Visual Studio Code (VS Code): Trnh son tho m ngun (IDE)

- Thng tin: VS Code l mt trnh son tho m ngun min ph, mnh m v rt ph bin, c pht trin bi Microsoft. N ni ting vi giao din trc quan, hiu sut tt v kh nng m rng cao thng qua cc extensions (tin ch m rng).
- Li ch cho d n ca bn:
  - H tr ngn ng tuyt vi: VS Code c h tr c php, gi  m (IntelliSense), debugging (g li) tch hp cho c JavaScript (React) v Python (Django). Bn c th ci t cc extension c th cho tng ngn ng  c tri nghim tt nht.
  - Terminal tch hp: Bn c th chy cc lnh terminal trc tip bn trong VS Code, rt tin li cho vic qun l d n React (v d: npm start, yarn start) v Django (v d: python manage.py runserver, python manage.py makemigrations).
  - Qun l Git tch hp: VS Code c tch hp sn cc tnh nng qun l Git, gip bn d dng commit, push, pull, branch, merge code.
  - Kh nng m rng: Cng ng VS Code rt ln v c v s extensions hu ch cho React (v d: ES7 React/Redux/GraphQL/React-Native snippets), Python (v d: Python), Django (v d: Django), v cc cng c khc (v d: Prettier cho formatting code, ESLint cho linting JavaScript).
  - Debugging mnh m: VS Code cung cp cc cng c debugging trc quan cho c JavaScript (Node.js, trnh duyt) v Python, gip bn d dng tm v sa li trong code.

MySQL: H qun tr c s d liu quan h (RDBMS)

- Thng tin: MySQL l mt h qun tr c s d liu m ngun m rt ph bin, c bit n vi tnh n nh,  tin cy v hiu sut tt. N lu tr d liu ca ng dng mt cch c cu trc, cho php bn truy vn v qun l d liu hiu qu.
- Vai tr trong d n ca bn:
  - Lu tr d liu ng dng: MySQL s c s dng  lu tr tt c cc d liu lin quan n ng dng "clone Spotify" ca bn, bao gm thng tin v bi ht, ngh s, album, ngi dng, playlist, lch s nghe nhc, v.v.
  - Tng tc thng qua Django ORM: Django cung cp mt Object-Relational Mapper (ORM), cho php bn tng tc vi c s d liu MySQL bng cch s dng cc lp v i tng Python, thay v vit trc tip cc cu lnh SQL phc tp. iu ny gip vic pht trin tr nn nhanh chng v d bo tr hn.
- Tch hp vi Django: Django c h tr tt cho MySQL. Bn s cn ci t driver kt ni MySQL cho Python (thng l mysqlclient) v cu hnh thng tin kt ni c s d liu (host, port, username, password, database name) trong file settings.py ca d n Django.

React: Th vin JavaScript cho xy dng giao din ngi dng (Frontend Library)

- Thng tin: React l mt th vin JavaScript m ngun m c pht trin bi Facebook (Meta). N tp trung vo vic xy dng cc thnh phn giao din ngi dng (UI components) c kh nng ti s dng, gip vic pht trin cc ng dng web phc tp tr nn d dng qun l v bo tr hn.
- Vai tr trong d n ca bn:
  - Xy dng giao din ngi dng tng tc: React s c s dng  to ra giao din ngi dng ng v tng tc cho ng dng "clone Spotify" ca bn. Ngi dng c th duyt th vin nhc, tm kim, to playlist, iu khin vic pht nhc, v.v. thng qua giao din ny.
  - Component-based architecture: React khuyn khch vic chia nh giao din thnh cc component nh, c lp v c th ti s dng. iu ny gip code d hiu, d bo tr v d pht trin hn.
  - Virtual DOM: React s dng mt c ch Virtual DOM  ti u ha vic cp nht giao din, ch thc hin cc thay i thc s cn thit trn DOM ca trnh duyt, gip ng dng chy mt m hn.
  - Tng tc vi Backend API: React s gi cc yu cu n API backend c xy dng bng Django  ly d liu (v d: danh sch bi ht, thng tin ngh s) v gi d liu (v d: to playlist mi).

Python: Ngn ng lp trnh a nng (Backend Language)

- Thng tin: Python l mt ngn ng lp trnh thng dch, cp cao, a nng v rt ph bin. N ni ting vi c php r rng, d c v mt h sinh thi th vin phong ph cho nhiu mc ch khc nhau.
- Vai tr trong d n ca bn:
  - Ngn ng chnh cho Backend: Python s l ngn ng chnh c s dng  xy dng logic nghip v ca backend, x l cc yu cu t frontend, tng tc vi c s d liu MySQL, v xy dng API.
  - H sinh thi Django: Python l nn tng ca framework Django, cung cp nhiu cng c v th vin mnh m cho vic pht trin web.

Django: Framework web cp cao ca Python (Backend Framework)

- Thng tin: Django l mt framework web m ngun m, cp cao, c vit bng Python. N tun theo kin trc Model-Template-View (MTV) v cung cp nhiu tnh nng "out-of-the-box" gip vic pht trin cc ng dng web phc tp tr nn nhanh chng v d dng hn.
- Vai tr trong d n ca bn:
  - Xy dng Backend API (vi Django REST Framework): Django kt hp vi Django REST Framework s gip bn xy dng cc API endpoints mnh m v d qun l  frontend React c th giao tip.
  - Qun l Models v tng tc vi Database: Django ORM gip bn nh ngha cu trc d liu (Models) v tng tc vi c s d liu MySQL mt cch d dng.
  - X l Routing (URLs): Django gip bn nh ngha cc URL ca ng dng v nh x chng n cc view (hm x l logic).
  - Qun l xc thc v phn quyn (nu cn): Django cung cp cc cng c tch hp  qun l ngi dng, xc thc v phn quyn truy cp.
  - Cu trc d n r rng: Django khuyn khch mt cu trc d n c t chc, gip bn d dng qun l v bo tr code.

Mi trng pht trin d kin:

- H iu hnh: Windows, macOS hoc Linux (VS Code h tr a nn tng).
- Python: c ci t trn h thng.
- pip: Trnh qun l gi ca Python  ci t Django v cc th vin khc (v d: mysqlclient, Django REST Framework).
- Node.js v npm (hoc yarn): Cn thit  qun l cc gi v chy ng dng React.
- MySQL Server: Ci t v cu hnh mt instance ca MySQL Server trn my ca bn hoc mt my ch khc.
- VS Code: Trnh son tho m ngun chnh.
- Cc extension VS Code: Ci t cc extension h tr cho Python, Django, React, JavaScript, Git, v cc cng c h tr khc.
- Virtual Environment (Python): Nn s dng virtual environment (v d: venv hoc conda)  qun l cc dependencies ca d n Python mt cch c lp.

## c t chc nng

Qun l Ngi dng (User Management)

- ng k ti khon (User Registration):
  - Ngi dng c th to ti khon mi bng cch cung cp cc thng tin:
    - Tn ngi dng (username) - _bt buc, duy nht_
    - a ch email (email) - _bt buc, nh dng hp l, duy nht_
    - Mt khu (password) - _bt buc, p ng cc yu cu v  di v  phc tp (nu c)_
  - H thng s xc thc d liu u vo.
  - Sau khi ng k thnh cng, ngi dng s c to mt ti khon mi trong h thng.
  - (Ty chn) H thng c th gi email xc thc ti khon.
- ng nhp (User Login):
  - Ngi dng c th ng nhp bng cch cung cp tn ngi dng hoc a ch email v mt khu  ng k.
  - H thng s xc thc thng tin ng nhp.
  - Sau khi ng nhp thnh cng, h thng s tr v mt token xc thc (v d: JWT - JSON Web Token)  ngi dng s dng cho cc yu cu API tip theo.
- ng xut (User Logout):
  - Ngi dng c th v hiu ha token xc thc hin ti.
- Qun mt khu (Forgot Password):
  - Ngi dng c th yu cu t li mt khu bng cch cung cp a ch email  ng k.
  - H thng s gi mt email cha lin kt hoc m t li mt khu n a ch email .
  - Ngi dng c th s dng lin kt/m  t li mt khu mi.

Duyt Danh Mc Nhc (Browse Music Catalog)

- Ly danh sch bi ht (Get Song List):
  - API cho php truy xut danh sch tt c cc bi ht c trong h thng (c th c phn trang).
  - C th h tr cc tham s truy vn  lc v sp xp (v d: theo tn bi ht, ngh s, album, ngy pht hnh).
- Ly thng tin chi tit bi ht (Get Song Details):
  - API cho php truy xut thng tin chi tit ca mt bi ht c th da trn ID ca bi ht. Thng tin c th bao gm tn bi ht, ngh s, album, nm pht hnh, th loi, ng dn file nhc.
- Ly danh sch ngh s (Get Artist List):
  - API cho php truy xut danh sch tt c cc ngh s c trong h thng (c th c phn trang).
- Ly thng tin chi tit ngh s (Get Artist Details):
  - API cho php truy xut thng tin chi tit ca mt ngh s c th da trn ID ca ngh s. Thng tin c th bao gm tn ngh s, tiu s (nu c), danh sch cc album v bi ht lin quan.
- Ly danh sch album (Get Album List):
  - API cho php truy xut danh sch tt c cc album c trong h thng (c th c phn trang).
- Ly thng tin chi tit album (Get Album Details):
  - API cho php truy xut thng tin chi tit ca mt album c th da trn ID ca album. Thng tin c th bao gm tn album, ngh s, nm pht hnh, danh sch cc bi ht trong album, nh ba.
- Ly danh sch th loi (Get Genre List):
  - API cho php truy xut danh sch tt c cc th loi nhc c trong h thng.
- Ly danh sch bi ht theo th loi (Get Songs by Genre):
  - API cho php truy xut danh sch cc bi ht thuc mt th loi c th.

Qun l Playlist (Playlist Management)

- To playlist (Create Playlist):
  - Ngi dng  xc thc c th to playlist mi bng cch cung cp tn cho playlist.
- Ly danh sch playlist ca ngi dng (Get User Playlists):
  - Ngi dng  xc thc c th truy xut danh sch tt c cc playlist m h  to.
- Ly thng tin chi tit playlist (Get Playlist Details):
  - Ngi dng  xc thc (hoc c quyn truy cp) c th truy xut thng tin chi tit ca mt playlist c th da trn ID ca playlist, bao gm tn playlist v danh sch cc bi ht trong .
- Thm bi ht vo playlist (Add Song to Playlist):
  - Ngi dng  xc thc c th thm mt bi ht c th (da trn ID bi ht) vo mt playlist m h s hu.
- Xa bi ht khi playlist (Remove Song from Playlist):
  - Ngi dng  xc thc c th xa mt bi ht c th khi mt playlist m h s hu.
- Cp nht thng tin playlist (Update Playlist Details):
  - Ngi dng  xc thc c th cp nht thng tin ca mt playlist m h s hu (v d: i tn playlist).
- Xa playlist (Delete Playlist):
  - Ngi dng  xc thc c th xa mt playlist m h s hu.

Lch S Pht Nhc (Playback History)

- Ghi li lch s pht nhc (Record Playback History):
  - Khi mt ngi dng  xc thc pht mt bi ht, h thng s ghi li thng tin v bi ht  v thi im pht.
- Ly lch s pht nhc ca ngi dng (Get User Playback History):
  - Ngi dng  xc thc c th truy xut lch s cc bi ht m h  nghe (c th c phn trang v gii hn s lng).
  - C th h tr lc theo khong thi gian.

Tm kim (Search)

- Tm kim tng qut (General Search):
  - API cho php ngi dng tm kim thng tin trong ton b h thng (bi ht, ngh s, album, playlist) da trn mt t kha.
  - Kt qu tm kim c th c nhm theo loi (v d: bi ht, ngh s, album).

Pht nhc (Playback - C th khng phi l API thun ty, nhng cn xem xt)

- (C th l mt endpoint  ly ng dn pht nhc): API c th cung cp mt endpoint tr v ng dn (URL) n file audio ca mt bi ht c th  client c th pht. Cn xem xt vn  bo mt v quyn truy cp.

# THIT K V PHN TCH DATABASE

## Bng users

- Mc ch: Lu tr thng tin v ngi dng ca ng dng.
- Cc ct:
  - id (INT, PRIMARY KEY, AUTO_INCREMENT - ngm nh): Kha chnh, nh danh duy nht cho mi ngi dng.
  - username (TEXT, NOT NULL, UNIQUE HASH): Tn ngi dng, bt buc v duy nht. S dng HASH index cho hiu sut truy vn tt khi tm kim theo tn ngi dng.
  - email (TEXT, NOT NULL, UNIQUE HASH): a ch email ca ngi dng, bt buc v duy nht. Tng t, HASH index gip tng tc  tm kim theo email.
  - password (TEXT, NOT NULL): Mt khu ca ngi dng (lu  cn c m ha an ton trc khi lu vo database).
  - profile_image_path (TEXT, DEFAULT NULL): ng dn n nh i din ca ngi dng (ty chn).
  - created_at (DATETIME, DEFAULT current_timestamp()): Thi im ngi dng to ti khon, t ng c gn gi tr thi gian hin ti khi mt bn ghi mi c thm vo.
  - isPremium (TINYINT(1), DEFAULT 0): Trng boolean (0 hoc 1) cho bit ngi dng c phi l ti khon premium hay khng (mc nh l khng).

Phn tch: Bng ny cha cc thng tin c bn cn thit  qun l ngi dng, bao gm thng tin ng nhp, thng tin c nhn ty chn v trng thi ti khon (premium/free).

## Bng songs

- Mc ch: Lu tr thng tin v cc bi ht trong th vin nhc.
- Cc ct:
  - id (INT, PRIMARY KEY, AUTO_INCREMENT - ngm nh): Kha chnh, nh danh duy nht cho mi bi ht.
  - title (TEXT, NOT NULL): Tiu  ca bi ht, bt buc.
  - duration (INT, DEFAULT NULL): Thi lng ca bi ht (c th tnh bng giy).
  - artist (TEXT, DEFAULT NULL): Tn ngh s trnh by bi ht.
  - genre_id (INT, DEFAULT NULL, FOREIGN KEY references genres): Kha ngoi, lin kt bi ht vi th loi ca n trong bng genres. Cho php mt bi ht thuc v mt th loi.
  - audio_file_path (TEXT, DEFAULT NULL): ng dn n file audio ca bi ht.
  - video_file_path (TEXT, DEFAULT NULL): ng dn n file video ca bi ht (ty chn).
  - image_file_path (TEXT, DEFAULT NULL): ng dn n nh ba ca bi ht (ty chn).
  - isPrenium (TINYINT(1), DEFAULT 0): Trng boolean cho bit bi ht ny c phi l ni dung premium hay khng (mc nh l khng).

Phn tch: Bng ny cha thng tin chi tit v mi bi ht, bao gm tiu , ngh s, thi lng, lin kt n th loi v cc ng dn n cc file media lin quan. Trng isPrenium cho php phn bit ni dung dnh cho ngi dng tr ph.

## Bng genres

- Mc ch: Lu tr thng tin v cc th loi nhc.
- Cc ct:
  - id (INT, PRIMARY KEY, AUTO_INCREMENT - ngm nh): Kha chnh, nh danh duy nht cho mi th loi.
  - name (TEXT, NOT NULL, UNIQUE HASH): Tn ca th loi, bt buc v duy nht. S dng HASH index  m bo tm kim v kim tra trng lp tn th loi hiu qu.

Bng ny n gin cha danh sch cc th loi nhc c trong h thng, m bo tnh nht qun khi gn th loi cho cc bi ht.

Bng playlists:

- Mc ch: Lu tr thng tin v cc playlist do ngi dng to.
- Cc ct:
  - id (INT, PRIMARY KEY, AUTO_INCREMENT - ngm nh): Kha chnh, nh danh duy nht cho mi playlist.
  - name (TEXT, NOT NULL): Tn ca playlist, bt buc.
  - user_id (INT, NOT NULL, FOREIGN KEY references users): Kha ngoi, lin kt playlist vi ngi dng  to n. Mt ngi dng c th to nhiu playlist.
  - created_at (DATETIME, DEFAULT current_timestamp()): Thi im playlist c to.

Bng ny lu tr thng tin c bn v cc playlist do ngi dng to v lin kt chng vi ngi to.

## Bng playlist_songs

- Mc ch: To mi quan h "nhiu-nhiu" gia bng playlists v bng songs. Mt playlist c th cha nhiu bi ht v mt bi ht c th thuc v nhiu playlist.
- Cc ct:
  - playlist_id (INT, NOT NULL, PRIMARY KEY, FOREIGN KEY references playlists): Kha ngoi, tham chiu n ID ca playlist.
  - song_id (INT, NOT NULL, PRIMARY KEY, FOREIGN KEY references songs): Kha ngoi, tham chiu n ID ca bi ht.
- Kha chnh phc hp (playlist_id, song_id): m bo rng mt bi ht ch xut hin mt ln trong mt playlist c th.

bng trung gian ny gii quyt mi quan h "nhiu-nhiu" gia playlist v bi ht, cho php ngi dng ty chnh ni dung playlist ca h.

## Bng favorite_songs

- Mc ch: Lu tr thng tin v cc bi ht yu thch ca ngi dng. To mi quan h "nhiu-nhiu" gia users v songs cho mc ch yu thch.
- Cc ct:
  - user_id (INT, NOT NULL, PRIMARY KEY, FOREIGN KEY references users): Kha ngoi, tham chiu n ID ca ngi dng.
  - song_id (INT, NOT NULL, PRIMARY KEY, FOREIGN KEY references songs): Kha ngoi, tham chiu n ID ca bi ht c yu thch.
  - liked_at (DATETIME, DEFAULT current_timestamp()): Thi im bi ht c ngi dng thm vo danh sch yu thch.
- Kha chnh phc hp (user_id, song_id): m bo rng mt ngi dng ch c th yu thch mt bi ht mt ln.

Bng ny cho php ngi dng nh du cc bi ht yu thch ca h v theo di thi im h thch chng.

Mi quan h gia cc bng:

- users mt-nhiu playlists (mt ngi dng c th to nhiu playlist).
- users nhiu-nhiu songs thng qua bng favorite_songs (mt ngi dng c th thch nhiu bi ht v mt bi ht c th c nhiu ngi dng thch).
- playlists nhiu-nhiu songs thng qua bng playlist_songs (mt playlist c th cha nhiu bi ht v mt bi ht c th thuc v nhiu playlist).
- genres mt-nhiu songs (mt th loi c th c nhiu bi ht).

# THIT K V CI T CHNG TRNH

## 1\. Backend (Python - Django)

- core/ (ng dng qun l ngi dng):  
  - models.py: nh ngha model User (tng ng bng users).
  - serializers.py: nh ngha UserSerializer (cho thng tin ngi dng), UserCreationSerializer (cho ng k), AuthTokenSerializer (cho ng nhp).
  - views.py: S dng ModelViewSet hoc APIView t DRF  cung cp cc API endpoints cho ng k, ng nhp, ly/cp nht thng tin ngi dng. C th s dng TokenObtainPairView t rest_framework_simplejwt cho JWT authentication.
  - urls.py: nh ngha cc URL patterns cho cc API lin quan n ngi dng (v d: /api/users/register/, /api/users/login/, /api/users/me/).
  - migrations/: Cha cc migrations cho model User.
  - admin.py: Cho php qun tr vin qun l ngi dng thng qua Django Admin.
- music/ (ng dng qun l nhc):  
  - models.py: nh ngha cc models:
    - Genre (tng ng bng genres).
    - Track (tng ng bng songs). Lu  tn model l Track thay v Song.
  - serializers.py: nh ngha GenreSerializer, TrackSerializer  chuyn i d liu gia models v JSON.
  - views.py: S dng ModelViewSet hoc ListAPIView, RetrieveAPIView  cung cp API endpoints cho vic lit k v xem chi tit th loi v bi ht. C th thm b lc v phn trang.
  - urls.py: nh ngha cc URL patterns cho cc API lin quan n th loi v bi ht (/api/music/genres/, /api/music/genres/{id}/tracks/, /api/music/tracks/, /api/music/tracks/{id}/).
  - migrations/: Cha cc migrations cho cc models nhc.
- playlists/ (ng dng qun l playlist):  
  - models.py: nh ngha cc models:
    - Playlist (tng ng bng playlists).
    - PlaylistTrack (tng ng bng playlist_songs - c th c thm trng order nu cn sp xp bi ht trong playlist). Lu  tn model.
  - serializers.py: nh ngha PlaylistSerializer, PlaylistTrackSerializer (c th dng  thm/xa bi ht).
  - views.py: S dng ModelViewSet  to, ly danh sch, ly chi tit, cp nht, xa playlist. Cung cp API endpoints  thm v xa bi ht khi playlist (c th l cc view ring hoc actions trong PlaylistViewSet). Yu cu xc thc ngi dng.
  - urls.py: nh ngha cc URL patterns cho cc API lin quan n playlist (/api/playlists/, /api/playlists/{id}/, /api/playlists/{id}/tracks/add/, /api/playlists/{id}/tracks/remove/).
  - migrations/: Cha cc migrations cho cc models playlist.
- favorite/ (ng dng qun l bi ht yu thch):  
  - models.py: nh ngha model FavoriteTrack (tng ng bng favorite_songs).
  - serializers.py: nh ngha FavoriteTrackSerializer.
  - views.py: Cung cp API endpoints  thm bi ht vo yu thch, xa bi ht khi yu thch, v ly danh sch cc bi ht yu thch ca ngi dng (yu cu xc thc). C th s dng ListCreateDestroyAPIView hoc ModelViewSet.
  - urls.py: nh ngha cc URL patterns cho cc API lin quan n yu thch (/api/favorites/, /api/favorites/{track_id}/).
  - migrations/: Cha cc migrations cho model FavoriteTrack.
- clonespotify_backend/ (Th mc d n chnh):  
  - settings.py: Cu hnh d n Django, bao gm database, ci t cc ng dng (core, music, playlists, favorite, rest_framework, rest_framework_simplejwt), middleware, CORS (nu frontend chy trn port khc), v.v.
  - urls.py: URL patterns gc ca d n, bao gm cc include()  dn n urls.py ca tng ng dng (v d: path('api/users/', include('core.urls')), path('api/music/', include('music.urls')), v.v.).
  - wsgi.py: im vo cho WSGI server.
  - asgi.py: im vo cho ASGI server.
  - \__init_\_.py: nh du th mc l mt Python package.

## 2\. FrontEnd (React)

- Component-Based Architecture: ng dng c xy dng da trn cc components ti s dng, gip qun l code d dng hn v tng tnh modularity.
- Routing: S dng mt th vin routing (thng l react-router-dom)  iu hng gia cc trang nh Trang ch, ng nhp, ng k, v cc trang qun l nhc/playlist. Cc routes c th c nh ngha trong th mc routes/ hoc trc tip trong App.js.
- Layouts: S dng cc layout components (ClientLayout, LoginLayout, AdminLayout)  nh hnh cu trc visual ca cc trang khc nhau. iu ny gip duy tr s nht qun v giao din.
- Pages: Cc trang (pages/Login, pages/Signup, pages/TrangChu, pages/QL_AudioMusic) s cha cc components v logic c th cho tng trang.
- State Management: ng dng c th s dng useState v useEffect cho state cc b trong components. i vi state ton cc (v d: thng tin ngi dng  ng nhp, danh sch nhc ang pht), c th s dng React Context API (trong th mc contexts/ ca Layouts) hoc mt th vin qun l state bn ngoi nh Redux hoc Zustand (nu ng dng phc tp).
- API Interaction: Th mc services/ chu trch nhim giao tip vi backend API Django. Cc hm trong y s thc hin cc HTTP requests n cc endpoints backend  ly v gi d liu lin quan n ngi dng, nhc, playlist, v.v. (s dng Axios hoc fetch).
- Authentication Flow: Cc components trong components/DangNhap/ v pages/Login/ s x l vic gi thng tin ng nhp n backend API (/api/users/login/). Sau khi ng nhp thnh cng, frontend s nhn token xc thc (JWT) v lu tr n (v d: trong Local Storage hoc mt state qun l authentication). Token ny s c gi km trong cc request tip theo n cc API c bo v. Tng t cho chc nng ng k (components/DangKy/ v pages/Signup/ gi /api/users/register/).
- Qun l Nhc v Playlist: Cc components v pages lin quan n nhc (trong components/ChucNang/ v pages/QL_AudioMusic/) s s dng cc hm trong services/music.js v services/playlists.js  tng tc vi cc API endpoints tng ng ca backend. iu ny bao gm vic hin th danh sch nhc, xem chi tit, to, sa, xa playlist, thm/xa bi ht khi playlist.
- Trang Ch: pages/TrangChu/ v cc components trong components/TrangChu/ s hin th ni dung chnh khi ngi dng truy cp ng dng ln u hoc sau khi ng nhp. Ni dung ny c th bao gm danh sch cc bi ht, album, ngh s ni bt (d liu ly t backend API).
- Global Styles: GlobalStyles.css v th mc GlobalStyles/ (nu c CSS-in-JS) nh ngha cc style chung cho ton b ng dng, m bo tnh nht qun v mt giao din.
- Utils: Cc hm tin ch trong utils/ c th c s dng  x l cc tc v lp i lp li hoc cc logic nh trong ng dng.

1. **GIAO DIN**
2. **CCH THC CI T**
3. **Ci t Backend**

Clone:

git clone <https://github.com/Tinhs05/CloneSpotify_Backend.git>

cd Spotify_BE

To v kch hot mi trng o:

python -m venv .venv

.venv\\Scripts\\activate

Ci t cc th vin cn thit:

pip install -r requirements.txt

Cu hnh database:

SQL: CREATE DATABASE musicapp;

settings.py:

DATABASES = {

'default': {

'ENGINE': 'django.db.backends.mysql',

'NAME': 'musicapp',

'USER': 'root',

'PASSWORD': '', # Nhp mt khu MySQL ca bn nu c

'HOST': 'localhost',

'PORT': '3307', # Port mc nh ca MySQL l 3306, hy kim tra li nu bn  thay i

}

}

To migrations

python src/manage.py makemigrations

p dng migrations

python src/manage.py migrate

To superuser

python src/manage.py createsuperuser

Chy server

python src/manage.py runserver

1. **Ci t FrontEnd**

npm start

# TNG KT

D n "clone Spotify" l mt n lc xy dng mt nn tng pht nhc trc tuyn, tng t nh Spotify, s dng cc cng ngh m ngun m mnh m l React cho giao din ngi dng, Python v framework Django cho backend. Mc tiu ca d n l to ra mt h thng cho php ngi dng ng k, ng nhp, duyt v tm kim th vin nhc, to v qun l playlist c nhn, cng nh tng tc vi cc tnh nng c bn ca mt ng dng nghe nhc hin i.

Thng qua vic pht trin API dch v bng Django REST Framework, d n cung cp mt backend mnh m v linh hot  qun l d liu ngi dng, danh mc nhc (bi ht, ngh s, album, th loi), playlist v lch s nghe. Frontend React ng vai tr l giao din tng tc trc quan, cho php ngi dng d dng truy cp v s dng cc chc nng ca nn tng.
